ck-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Equally as impressive, is that the salt mines were still operational until only a few decades ago.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Entrance fee &amp; getting there<\/strong><br>The mines are about 35 minutes out of Krakow. You can make your way there yourself by car or public transport (50 min) or alternatively book onto a fully guided tour from Krakow.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/krakow-wieliczka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Order your entrance ticket here<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/wielizcka-full-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">easily do a tour from Krakow<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110642\/Wieliczka-Salt-Mine-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Wieliczka Salt Mine\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Wieliczka Salt Mine\" data-id=\"44996\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110642\/Wieliczka-Salt-Mine.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=44996\" class=\"wp-image-44996 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110642\/Wieliczka-Salt-Mine-540x810.jpg 