n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-9-bernatek-footbridge\">9. Bernatek Footbridge<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>From the Jewish district, cross the river via the popular Bernatek Footbridge. This romantic bridge is a pedestrian and bike only bridge, decorated with acrobatic figures that hang from the bridge&#x2019;s cables.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110820\/krakow-poland-Bernatek-Footbridge-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"krakow poland Bernatek Footbridge\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"krakow poland Bernatek Footbridge\" data-id=\"44804\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110820\/krakow-poland-Bernatek-Footbridge.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=44804\" class=\"wp-image-44804 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110820\/krakow-poland-Bernatek-Footbridge-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110820\/krakow-poland-Bernatek-Footbridge-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110820\/krakow-poland-Bernatek-Footbridge-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110820\/krakow-poland-Bernatek-Footbridge-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110820\/krakow-poland-Bernatek-Footbridge-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110820\/krakow-poland-Bernatek-Footbridge-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/up