rch Eglise Saint-Joseph can&#x2019;t be missed when exiting the Bernatek footbridge. The imposing 80-meter high clock tower, and beautiful design of the church, is visible from all over Krakow. The small square with a park and benches, in front of the church, is also a wonderful place to sit down.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>See all:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/krakow-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">all hotels in Krakow<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110849\/krakow-things-to-do-E%CC%81glise-Saint-Joseph.jpg\" alt=\"krakow things to do E&#x301;glise Saint Joseph\" class=\"wp-image-44784\"><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-day-3-auschwitz-and-kopiec-krakusa\">Day 3 &#x2013; Auschwitz and Kopiec Krakusa<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-11-auschwitz-concentration-camp\">11. Auschwitz Concentration Camp<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/poland\/auschwitz-birkenau\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Auschwitz-Birkenau<\/a> was the largest Nazi concentration camp, where Jews, Gypsies, Jehovah, Polish, Hungarians, and more were deported. Between 1940 and 1945 over 1.2 million people were gassed and burned at Auschwitz-Birkenau and it became one of the greatest mass murders in human history.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <d