rest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110843\/poland-Auschwitz-Concentration-Camp-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-12-sunset-at-kopiec-krakusa-great-thing-to-do-in-krakow\">12. Sunset at Kopiec Krakusa &#x2013; Great Thing to do in Krakow<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Close-off your day, and trip in Krakow, with some good vibes, by experiencing the sunset on top of Kopiec hill. It is a lovely hilltop park that overlooks the old town. Many locals come here to relax and walk their dogs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How to get there:<\/strong>&#xA0;<br>From the old town, either get an Uber (10 min), use scooters such as Lime (25 min) or by tram (27 min).&#xA0;&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110720\/krakow-poland-Kopiec-Krakusa-sunset.jpg\" alt=\"krakow poland Kopiec Krakusa sunset\"><\/noscript><img width=\"440\" height=\"338\" alt=\"krakow poland Kopiec Krakusa sunset\" class=\"wp-image-44854 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110720\/krakow-poland-Kopiec-Krakusa-sunset.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110720\/krakow-poland-Kopiec-Krakusa-sunset-300x230.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110720\/krakow-poland-Kopiec-Krakusa-sunset-600x461.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110720\/krakow-poland-Kopiec-Krakusa-sunset-781x600.jpg 781w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/23110720\/krakow-poland-Kopiec-Krakusa-sun